{"tid":2183754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（軟實力）武漢肺炎大爆發，東方某国完全唔識借此機會，發揚軟實力，結果俾西方又建立起新風氣","createTime":"2020-09-01T06:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T06:20:42.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62d8f1033b49c1b2984aa5e2afa81df324850890","tid":2183754,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"好耐之前，本人寫過一篇關於軟實力嘅文章：<br />\n<br />\n（軟實力）喺現在社會，支那軟實力係等於零<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bEEvsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bEEvsS</a><br />\n<br />\n而家武漢肺炎大爆發，東方某国完全唔識借此機會，發揚軟實力。<br />\n<br />\n西方社會借此機會，創立及帶動新風氣。<br />\n因為武漢肺炎，於西方社會，人同人見面時，唔再握手，改為碰肘（elbow bump）。<br />\n<br />\n此動作由西方人發明，連東方某大国嘅外長，亦盲目跟隨此風。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/202008291401339121_AG099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F202008291401339121_AG099.jpg&h=cac380ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/202008291401341681_08620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F202008291401341681_08620.jpg&h=153ade6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.oushinet.com/u/cms/www/image/20200827/20200827205555_934.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oushinet.com%2Fu%2Fcms%2Fwww%2Fimage%2F20200827%2F20200827205555_934.jpg&h=84c58630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方某某大国，又話要有「文化自信」「制度自信」「理論自信」「道路自信」？<br />\n<br />\n自己跟隨人地個套。人地個一套，靜雞雞入侵你嘅生活，你仲要懞下懞下，死跟而不自知。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：可憐呀.jpg"}]}